# Source Tiers & Reliability

## Tier 1 - API-Backed (Highest Reliability)

| Source | API Type | Rate Limit | Best For |
|--------|----------|------------|----------|
| PubMed | E-utilities | 3/10 req/s | MeSH-indexed biomedical lit |
| CrossRef | REST | 50 req/s | DOI resolution, metadata |
| bioRxiv | API | 10 req/s | Biology preprints |

## Tier 2 - Semi-Structured

| Source | Method | Reliability | Best For |
|--------|--------|-------------|----------|
| Semantic Scholar | API + scrape | High | Citation graph |
| medRxiv | API | Medium | Medical preprints |

## Tier 3 - Scraped (Last Resort)

| Source | Method | Reliability | Best For |
|--------|--------|-------------|----------|
| Google Scholar | Scraped | Variable | Broad academic search |
| CNKI | Manual | Low | Chinese literature |
